{"TopicId":157517,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Constellations","CreatedByName":"themonk","CreatedById":59409,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-09T09:04:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"themonk","CreatedById":59409,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-09T09:04:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe other day I got caught in a situation with a rover where I couldn\u0027t see a Target marker on the maneuvering ball, because it was pointed vertically. (didn\u0027t have anything mounted on the front of the rover to do a control-by from, to give me a horizontal view).\u00A0 So I picked a couple of stars to guide me in the right direction.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis got me to thinking...\u00A0 Are the stars fixed in the sky?\u00A0 If I look in the same direction will I always the the same stars and constellation? \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd, has anyone gone to the trouble to actually map constellations and give them names?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoy, I ask a lot of questions...\u00A0 But I\u0027m a curious guy!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-09T09:22:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey call this skybox. A fixed texture with stars and galaxies placed on the sky.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA skybox can be set with Texture Replacer. (Search for \u0022skybox\u0022 in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E of the thread)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/96851-11-texturereplacer-2413-442016/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/96851-11-texturereplacer-2413-442016/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;comment=2948306\u0026amp;embedComment=2948306\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-03-09T09:24:08Z\u0022 title=\u002203/09/2017 09:24  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 9, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-09T10:23:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere should be a small arrow on navball that indicates where your target marker is. If you didn\u0027t rotate the command module, (here goes my theory, I can\u0027t test it right now) then when the arrow is pointing upwards, you\u0027re going in correct direction.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"themonk","CreatedById":59409,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-09T12:41:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222980528\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157517\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221489051376\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey call this skybox. A fixed texture with stars and galaxies placed on the sky.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA skybox can be set with Texture Replacer. (Search for \u0022skybox\u0022 in the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E of the thread)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh....\u00A0 So the sky IS just a texture...\u00A0\u00A0 That would mean that there ARE Constellations that never change!\u00A0 Now all i have to do is find the Kerbal equivalent of the Big Dipper....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-09T15:17:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222980522\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157517\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221489050270\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002259409\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022themonk\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, themonk said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I picked a couple of stars to guide me in the right direction.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have done this \u003Cem\u003Emany\u003C/em\u003E times while rovering on the Mun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hotel26","CreatedById":139095,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-06T07:43:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222980601\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157517\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221489063275\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002259409\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022themonk\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/9/2017 at 8:41 PM, themonk said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow all i have to do is find the Kerbal equivalent of the Big Dipper....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn here(?):\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00225kFh9b0.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002290.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/5kFh9b0.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022qRvdz5N.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002273.99\u0022 height=\u0022128\u0022 width=\u0022173\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/qRvdz5N.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}